Name: Mini Skid Steer w/ Wheels
Description: Compact zero turn wheel loader built around the mini bobcat model. Excels on concrete and asphalt for clean ups, interior demolition, and landscaping where low ground disturbance matters. Includes general bucket, with pallet forks available for moving blocks and pallets.

Name: Mini excavator
Description: Compact zero tail excavator built on the JCB 18z1 platform. Designed for tight access trenching, garden works, and small demolition. Rubber tracks protect paving and offer confident digging for footings and services. Quick to transport and ideal where larger units cannot fit.

Name: Medium Bobcat Skid Steer w/ Tracks
Description: Track loader based on the T450 Bobcat model, built for sand, clay, and uneven terrain. Offers outstanding traction and stability for grading, backfilling, and moving bulk materials without tearing up the site. Compatible with tooth bucket or forks for all round site work.

Name: Larger Bobcat Skid Steer w/ Tracks
Description: High power track loader using the T190 Bobcat model. Strong hydraulics and lift capacity make it ideal for heavier pallets and bulk earthmoving. Performs reliably on steep or soft ground, maintaining productivity in demanding conditions including grading, pad prep, and material handling.

Name: Medium Excavator
Description: Mid size excavator built on the E80 Bobcat chassis. Offers deeper trenching capacity, strong digging force, and long reach for footings and truck loading. Balanced and fuel efficient for residential and medium size commercial sites needing compact but powerful performance.

Name: Large Excavator
Description: Heavy duty excavator using the JCB 85z1 model. Offers strong breakout force, excellent stability, and efficient cycle times for major excavation, demolition, and site development. Ideal when consistent power and reach are required on challenging terrain.

Name: Telehandler
Description: All terrain telehandler designed around the Bobcat TL619 model. Precise boom control for lifting pallets to upper floors and rooflines even on uneven ground. Ideal for masonry, timber, and steel material handling, with stable performance across demanding worksites.

Name: Compactor
Description: Reliable plate compactor powered by the Crommelins CC60RP model. Produces dense, level surfaces for driveways, patios, and trench backfill. Compact and easy to handle around forms and edges, making it efficient for small to medium site works.

Name: Concrete mixer
Model: Electric Semi-Automatic 200 Litre Mini Concrete Mixer
Description: Electric 200 litre mixer built on the Electric Semi Automatic 200 Litre model. Delivers consistent batches for small and medium concrete works including footings, slabs, and blockwork. Durable drum and simple controls keep crews productive with minimal downtime.

Name: Hole Boring Machine
Description: Petrol post hole digger using the VEVOR 63cc model. Performs fast and clean fence and footing holes even in firm ground. Includes auger and extensions ideal for posts, pergolas, decks, and tree planting on residential sites and small farms.

Name: Petrol Powerwasher
Description: A high-performance pressure washer for tough cleaning jobs. Ideal for removing dirt, grime, and paint from concrete, building exteriors, and heavy machinery, leaving surfaces looking like new.

Name: 3500 Tipper Truck w/ Driver
Description: Versatile 3.5 ton tipper built on the Mercedes chassis, ideal for tight access sites and daily material runs. The hydraulic tipper body unloads sand, soil, rubble, and aggregates quickly, improving productivity and reducing manual handling.

Name: 3500 Tipper w/ Crane and Driver
Description: Heavy duty 3.5 ton Isuzu truck fitted with a Fassi crane for precise lifting. Ideal for placing pallets, timber, steel, and packaged materials exactly where needed on site. The integrated tipper body allows efficient dual use for hauling and offloading.

Name: 16m3 Truck with Driver
Description: Large capacity tipper truck built on a Volvo 20 ton platform. Designed for bulk earthmoving, demolition waste, gravel, and high volume transport. The 16m3 body supports fast loading cycles, while the Volvo chassis provides stability and safety over longer hauls.

Name: Ride-Behind Skid Steer Mini
Description: Compact ride-behind skid steer designed for tight access jobs and surface-sensitive areas. Ideal for landscaping, clean-up works, and interior or urban sites where maneuverability and low ground disturbance are essential. Compatible with bucket and light attachments.

Name: Micro Excavator
Description: Ultra-compact micro excavator built for confined spaces and precision digging. Suitable for small trenching, drainage works, garden projects, and access-restricted areas where standard excavators cannot operate.

Name: Mini Dumper w/ Loading Bucket
Description: Compact mini dumper equipped with a front loading bucket for efficient material transport. Ideal for moving soil, rubble, and aggregates on residential sites, renovations, and narrow access jobs.

Name: Concrete Projection Gun
Description: Concrete projection gun model Koine 35 Evo designed for applying mortar and concrete in repair, reinforcement, and finishing works. Commonly used for structural repairs, shotcrete applications, and surface reinforcement on construction sites.

Name: ZZZ Internal Test Machine (€1 - Do Not Rent)
Description: Internal listing to verify Stripe production checkout. Not available for hire. Charges kept at €1 per day with a €1 deposit for testing. Remove after validation.
